Synopsis: Get all custom property values for a repository
Description:
Gets all custom property values that are set for a repository.
Users with read access to the repository can use this endpoint.
Notes: [Get all custom property values for a repository](https://docs.github.com/rest/repos/custom-properties#get-all-custom-property-values-for-a-repository)

Examples.Title: EXAMPLE 1
Examples.Code:
Get-GitHubRepositoryCustomProperty -Owner 'octocat' -Repository 'hello-world'
Gets all custom property values that are set for the 'hello-world' repository.
